Build this source how-to:
1) Get cyanogenmod sources:
      repo init -u git://github.com/CyanogenMod/android.git -b gingerbread
      repo sync
2) Copy sources to *source_home*/device/zte/v9plus
3) Initialize build environment:
      source build/envsetup.sh
      lunch full_v9plus-eng
4) Build sources:
      source build/tools/device/makerecoveries.sh full_v9plus-eng
5) Get your recovery.img from *source_home*/out/target/product/v9plus/ 

Full guide (Porting Clockwork Recovery to New Devices): http://www.koushikdutta.com/2010/10/porting-clockwork-recovery-to-new.html